<i>adjective</i>: 따끔하다 [따끔하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따끔하다 [따끔하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smarting; hot</dd><br>
<dd>따가울 정도로 몹시 덥다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a very hot, smarting feeling continuously.</dd><br>
<dd>2. guilty</dd><br>
<dd>마음의 자극을 받아 찔리는 듯한 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>To feel guilty as one's heart is stimulated.</dd><br>
<dd>3. painful</dd><br>
<dd>찔리거나 꼬집히는 것처럼 아프다.</dd><br>
<dd>To have a hurtful feeling like being poked or pinched continuously.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>